{"tid":736582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學 有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪","createTime":"2018-07-10T10:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T18:54:45.000Z","uid":131369,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19c3d7dab5f7ff4d4deb38f213a456e28cddfaa0","tid":736582,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n<br />\n「你癡左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n<br />\n成個小醜咁係到穀佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我Hi Hi, 牙都甩埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"78a5a05749167bb78f942950472ad31b9bc4ac0c","tid":736582,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9009de61d1c46940e80e8c053e3b83da4499d1e5","tid":736582,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"又loop"},{"pid":"c035542d37547baf3f8602bdc231e6df803af3cb","tid":736582,"uid":8009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"讀高雷預左"},{"pid":"72406af08da11d43caf73c5600749fdfdf94f876","tid":736582,"uid":129658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"次次都有睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d6b14260dde8678db87b908d190d5a4d927d7a","tid":736582,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike"